OL,4,CTalbot Green shooting
OL,6,FA sixth person has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder after a woman was shot dead in
OL,8,FTalbot Green.
OL,10,FJoanne Penney, 40, died after being
OL,11,Fshot in the chest at an address in
OL,12,FLlys Illtyd, Talbot Green, Rhondda
OL,13,FCynon Taf, on 9 March. In a statement
OL,14,Fat the time police said the incident
OL,15,Fmay be a case of mistaken identity.
OL,17,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,18,Fto find Ms Penney with serious
OL,19,Finjuries and she was pronounced dead.
