OL,6,FOn Wednesday, June 25, 21-year-old
OL,7,FKistina Ginova from Leicestershire,
OL,8,Fwho had previously been charged with
OL,9,Fassisting an offender, was charged
OL,10,Fwith murder.
OL,12,FGinova will stand trial in October
OL,13,Falong with seven other defendants in
OL,14,Fconnection with Joanne's death.
OL,16,FIn a tribute, Ms Penney's family said:
OL,17,F"We are devastated by the tragic loss
OL,18,Fof our beloved Joanne. She was a
OL,19,Fdaughter, mother, sister and niece `
OL,20,Floved deeply by all who knew her.
